text: @FedEx @FedExHelp unacceptable - I had to call you all to find out that your system is showing inaccurate info.  My whole week is now messed up because I won’t receive my items until a day later from what your REAL TIME tracking shows.  Why do you send an item to another state? https://t.co/JaSQMRGw3J
@revrobrodriguez Hi, this is David. I'm happy to help. Please dm your name, delivery address, and phone number so I can assist.

@FedExHelp I already called customer service, and they told me there’s nothing that they can do - it’s out of their hands. I think it’s ridiculous that your system is displaying wrong info. when you’re a billion-dollar company and you messed up my entire week’s schedule.
